    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName> filio <persName>bone memorie
                                <name ref="Natalis">Natali</name></persName> riceve da <persName
                            ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>, gratia Dei huius
                        sancte Lucane ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>, per
                        cartula livellario nomine (…), una <rs key="#Petiae">petia de terra</rs>,
                        quod est <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs>, et una <rs key="#Petiae">petia de
                            terra</rs> ille in loco <placeName ref="#places/473"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine">Lunata</placeName>,
                        pertenentes ecclesie <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3304"
                            key="#Baptismal_churches">Sancti Fridiani de ipso loco Lunata</orgName>,
                        quod est <rs key="#Baptismal_churches">plebem baptismalis</rs>, qui est de
                        subpotestatem ecclesie <rs key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>; et <rs key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">est
                            tenentes ipse petia de terra</rs>, quod est vinea, uno capo cum uno lato
                        in <rs key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions">terra</rs> suprascripti <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3304"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions">Sancti Fridiani</orgName>,
                        alio capo tenet in <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Wine #Priests"><name ref="Adalmarius"
                                >Adalmari</name></persName>
                        <rs>presbiteri</rs>, alio lato tenet in <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions">terra</rs> qui fuit <persName
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions">quondam <name ref="Deusdedit"
                                >Deusdedi</name></persName>; et ille alia petia de terra, es
                        tenentes uno capo cum uno lato in <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, alio
                        capo cum uno lato tenet in <rs key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        qui fuit <persName key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions">quondam <name
                                ref="Gastaldulus">Gastalduli</name></persName>; iamdicta petia de
                        terra (…) et predicta petia de terra qualiter ab omnis parte circumdate sunt
                        per designates locas, quas ipse vinea est per mensura ad iusta perticha
                        mensurata <rs key="#Size">sistariorum sex</rs> et ipse terra est per mensura
                        ad iusta perticha mensurata <rs key="#Size">sistariorum duo</rs> (…); simul
                        et dedisti mihi una petia de terra quod est <rs key="#Forests">silva</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Chestnuts">castagneto</rs> in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Confinia #Forests #Chestnuts #Fiscal_property #Mention"
                            ref="#places/3325">Cerquieto, ubi vocitatur Vivario</placeName>,
                        pertenentes suprascripte <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3304"
                            key="#Petiae #Forests #Chestnuts">ecclesie Sancti Fridiani</orgName>, es
                            <rs key="#Confinia">tenentes uno capo</rs> in <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions">terra</rs> et <rs key="#Forests"
                            >silva</rs> suprascripte <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3304"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Forests #Chestnuts">ecclesie
                            Sancti Fridiani</orgName>, alio capo tenet in <placeName key="#Rivers"
                                ><rs key="#Rivers">rivo qui dicitur Silani</rs></placeName>, lato
                        uno tenet in terra quod est <rs key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Mention"
                            >silva <rs key="#Emperor/king">domni regi</rs></rs>, alio lato tenet in
                            <rs key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions">terra</rs> suprascripte <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3304"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions">ecclesie Sancti
                            Fridiani</orgName>: suprascripta petia de terra quod est silva, qualiter
                        circumdata est per designatas locas, in integrum mihi dedisti (…). Obbligo:
                        ego vel meus heredes suprascripte petie de terre et vinee seo silve (…) bene
                        laborare seo meliorare debeamus privatum abendum (…). Censo: pro omni censum
                        et iustitia exinde tibi vel ad subcessoribus tuis ad pars ipsius ecclesie
                        Sancti Fridiani per singulos annos, in mense november, censum vobis reddere
                        debeaums ad suprascripta ecclesia Sancti Fridiani, per nos aut per misso
                        nostro vobis vel ad ministerialem illo quas ibi pre tempore ordinatus fuerit
                        argentum denarios duodecim boni expendivilis tantum (…). Pena: spondeo ego
                        qui supra Leo una cum meis heredes componere tibi (…) penam argentum soledos
                        viginti (…). <persName key="#Writer #Witness #Notary"><name
                                ref="Teudemundus">Teudimundus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Lambertus">Lambertu</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/150">Fraolmi</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudebertus">Teupertus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Deusdedit"
                            >Deusdedi</name></persName>, </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
